{"id": "ChIJoUgHHADHwoARxf2wW6hRz4A", "rating": 4.3, "userRatingCount": 282, "displayName": {"text": "ONE PIECE CAFE", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJoUgHHADHwoARxf2wW6hRz4A/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s5TWEweDZjMGs0Vm5aUWFFUTRaVGhyWTIxUVJtYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Amazing food and amazing experience! From the moment I walked in, I was greeted by Jessica (who was incredibly helpful and explained everything about the cafe! She recommended the Robin refresher and Brook’s curry (both of which were delicious!) The katsu curry was so delicious that I ran out of curry! (Compliments to chef Ben!) I arrived after the evening dinner rush and I really enjoyed listening to different one piece opening songs and watching the screen cycle through different one piece character graphics! Overall, I had an amazing time and I’ll definitely be coming back! Thank you Jessica and Ben for the great service and the great food!! 11/10 experience!!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Amazing food and amazing experience! From the moment I walked in, I was greeted by Jessica (who was incredibly helpful and explained everything about the cafe! She recommended the Robin refresher and Brook’s curry (both of which were delicious!) The katsu curry was so delicious that I ran out of curry! (Compliments to chef Ben!) I arrived after the evening dinner rush and I really enjoyed listening to different one piece opening songs and watching the screen cycle through different one piece character graphics! Overall, I had an amazing time and I’ll definitely be coming back! Thank you Jessica and Ben for the great service and the great food!! 11/10 experience!!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Trent G", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114238235865279083433/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXxq4QkgnbiSfkmQ-mBM1BTJQ4FIyStUD67gcUvap2Ms00x6dc=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-17T03:10:01.291681124Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s5TWEweDZjMGs0Vm5aUWFFUTRaVGhyWTIxUVJtYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s5TWEweDZjMGs0Vm5aUWFFUTRaVGhyWTIxUVJtYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c7001c0748a1:0x80cf51a85bb0fdc5"}, {"name": "places/ChIJoUgHHADHwoARxf2wW6hRz4A/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25aUGFuaHVVMjgxY1hGeGIydE1UREpvV0VGWGVYYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Awesome experience for food lovers and anime watchers alike, as myself never seeing the full anime I enjoyed the food plenty and how awesome the atmosphere/ art was rendered. As for my significant other he not only loved how nostalgic the cafe was for him as growing up watching the show but also loved and enjoyed his food too. We spent right around 80$~ but for the experience, decor, and food amount we believe that was a reasonable place to charge considering it is in the heart of LA. And lastly we did not knowing how seating worked, seating is limited inside the cafe and is first come first serve and there is not much “service” because it is like your typical order at the counter and pick up at the counter but the order takers were pleasant as well.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Awesome experience for food lovers and anime watchers alike, as myself never seeing the full anime I enjoyed the food plenty and how awesome the atmosphere/ art was rendered. As for my significant other he not only loved how nostalgic the cafe was for him as growing up watching the show but also loved and enjoyed his food too. We spent right around 80$~ but for the experience, decor, and food amount we believe that was a reasonable place to charge considering it is in the heart of LA. And lastly we did not knowing how seating worked, seating is limited inside the cafe and is first come first serve and there is not much “service” because it is like your typical order at the counter and pick up at the counter but the order takers were pleasant as well.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Katelyn Z.", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106047943790239417686/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUI_snZlV3l-Irm3pBSsBMMCbt4HrNw7A-u8ve9kCgE9Hlf9zle=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-25T01:28:46.484023866Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25aUGFuaHVVMjgxY1hGeGIydE1UREpvV0VGWGVYYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25aUGFuaHVVMjgxY1hGeGIydE1UREpvV0VGWGVYYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c7001c0748a1:0x80cf51a85bb0fdc5"}, {"name": "places/ChIJoUgHHADHwoARxf2wW6hRz4A/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t0SVpFTmxTMlF0UmpoaU1VdFBTMWR2VkdSb1lVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "It was a really fun experience. You felt like you were in the Sunny 🌞. The food was really good. I got the curry! Great service too. The gentleman upfront was very kind and made great conversation. Would definitely recommend for One Piece fans and all alike!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "It was a really fun experience. You felt like you were in the Sunny 🌞. The food was really good. I got the curry! Great service too. The gentleman upfront was very kind and made great conversation. Would definitely recommend for One Piece fans and all alike!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "RAUL TBAR", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112680515639697614504/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJt5jfElYG7G8bmC5jY1F1v8VElsAs8O9Uh5-hf3harb8FELA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-26T09:15:58.229457766Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t0SVpFTmxTMlF0UmpoaU1VdFBTMWR2VkdSb1lVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t0SVpFTmxTMlF0UmpoaU1VdFBTMWR2VkdSb1lVRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c7001c0748a1:0x80cf51a85bb0fdc5"}, {"name": "places/ChIJoUgHHADHwoARxf2wW6hRz4A/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21KT1ZtcGZURlptUzFKdWRXaHFZV3RzZERoaFQzYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Loved visiting here! The theming/atmosphere is super fun! Lots of screens showing various animations to make the experience immersive. There’s something to look at everywhere.\n\nService: Great! The security worker is very friendly with showing people in, busing tables, and checking on everyone. The counter staff are very patient with folks like me who are geeking out. ;)\n\nFood: The katsu curry was delicious and I’m still craving it days later. My bf got the burger (with an extra patty) and said it was very good. I think the portions were perfect.\n\nDrinks: I got and loved the Jinbe slushy, and my bf got the ube horchata. He raved about how good it was!\n\nWait/seating: We arrived at 11:15am on a Saturday and there was already a line. Took about 15min to get to order, and another 15 for food to be ready. We were very lucky and got indoor seating. There is a standing counter around a column inside, if no tables open up. Considering the quality of the food, atmosphere, and the popularity, I think the wait, and the prices, are reasonable.\n\nAlso, great merch! I restrained myself and only got two things, haha\n\nWe will come back! Thank you for making this such a fun and yummy place to visit.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Loved visiting here! The theming/atmosphere is super fun! Lots of screens showing various animations to make the experience immersive. There’s something to look at everywhere.\n\nService: Great! The security worker is very friendly with showing people in, busing tables, and checking on everyone. The counter staff are very patient with folks like me who are geeking out. ;)\n\nFood: The katsu curry was delicious and I’m still craving it days later. My bf got the burger (with an extra patty) and said it was very good. I think the portions were perfect.\n\nDrinks: I got and loved the Jinbe slushy, and my bf got the ube horchata. He raved about how good it was!\n\nWait/seating: We arrived at 11:15am on a Saturday and there was already a line. Took about 15min to get to order, and another 15 for food to be ready. We were very lucky and got indoor seating. There is a standing counter around a column inside, if no tables open up. Considering the quality of the food, atmosphere, and the popularity, I think the wait, and the prices, are reasonable.\n\nAlso, great merch! I restrained myself and only got two things, haha\n\nWe will come back! Thank you for making this such a fun and yummy place to visit.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Alison Carter", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115938920382870593708/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV3c8AdESduRQGJsC6z4bfROaMAUVuT4P6Nj1yHYYI2SXAfOayM=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-13T23:54:01.202808736Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21KT1ZtcGZURlptUzFKdWRXaHFZV3RzZERoaFQzYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21KT1ZtcGZURlptUzFKdWRXaHFZV3RzZERoaFQzYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c7001c0748a1:0x80cf51a85bb0fdc5"}, {"name": "places/ChIJoUgHHADHwoARxf2wW6hRz4A/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21WQlZTMWxWRXBwZWpObFExSllRMXAyZVU1M1JsRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Super cool spot to dine in or just stop by in to check out. We stopped by on our way to explore Little Tokyo. They have an ube horchata that was pretty good. The only thing is that they do not do any substitutions so I could not get a drink with non-dairy milk. The vibes are awesome though. Great One Piece themed decor and definitely cooler than some other themed cafes that I have been to.\n\nNow for my standard comments. The location is clean and well kept. Comfortable indoor seating.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Super cool spot to dine in or just stop by in to check out. We stopped by on our way to explore Little Tokyo. They have an ube horchata that was pretty good. The only thing is that they do not do any substitutions so I could not get a drink with non-dairy milk. The vibes are awesome though. Great One Piece themed decor and definitely cooler than some other themed cafes that I have been to.\n\nNow for my standard comments. The location is clean and well kept. Comfortable indoor seating.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Christine L", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106022290391959656407/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXVKvX7LlsjMqBRdnNW0s24q0E_Wyql353l49GQFDMZglJ3-Mi6=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-08T03:54:02.601256691Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21WQlZTMWxWRXBwZWpObFExSllRMXAyZVU1M1JsRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21WQlZTMWxWRXBwZWpObFExSllRMXAyZVU1M1JsRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c7001c0748a1:0x80cf51a85bb0fdc5"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJoUgHHADHwoARxf2wW6hRz4A/photos/AWCwydgHPmSxlQvyh1OqgrPs56DTVf4ovjhYLDXAvx49qeE0CiJxaHEELsI5NPnHFNe7UP8npPKipI7d5fgZKYCrpjdtq-qAnyBbFzgKevzOAhSBhHWKir2M66PXu9001JEgNvvcvSgQPHXaLIMhAnePPbG3WPO_gCd6meGvBfJwk5q1Wutm9T7HnSUAuYG4vfpIlS6i62fkPnUvbMR07J9IAvDnEUS5HhLd3sZ183zdyRjT